{
  "ref": "head-butler",
  "categoryRef": "npc",
  "title": "Head Butler",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Standard dialogue",
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Initial dialogue",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Head Butler",
                  "text": "After all that, are you sure I can't convince you to join the union?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Actually, I was wondering if..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Head Butler",
                  "text": "Kuani! I'll need to run and grab my forms, but if you wait there just a moment..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I was going to ask if you had any spare equipment..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Head Butler",
                  "text": "Spare equipment?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I may have a need to mask my identity again in the future... or perhaps carry a tray around."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Head Butler",
                  "text": "You're certain you don't want to join the union as well?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I'm sure."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Head Butler",
                  "text": "I see. In that case, which equipment would you like?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "The ram mask."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Thanks!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "The wolf mask."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Thanks!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "The bird mask."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Thanks!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "The jaguar mask."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Thanks!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "The snake mask."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Thanks!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "The butler's tray."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Thanks!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "None of them."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Head Butler",
                  "text": "Very well."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Subsequent dialogue",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Head Butler",
                  "text": "Changed your mind about joining the union? Or are you just after more equipment?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Just the equipment please."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Head Butler",
                  "text": "I see. In that case, what do you need?"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "dialogues": []
    }
  ]
}